---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="页面未找到"
  description="404 - 页面未找到"
>
  <div class="text-center py-20">
    <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">404</h1>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">页面未找到</h2>
    <p class="text-muted mb-8">
      抱歉，您访问的页面不存在或已被移动。
    </p>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-colors"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
        </svg>
        返回首页
      </a>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-2">或者访问：</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/blog" class="text-link hover:underline">文章</a>
          <a href="/tags" class="text-link hover:underline">标签</a>
          <a href="/archive" class="text-link hover:underline">归档</a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-link hover:underline">关于</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>